game.name: Prince Run
game.description:
This prince is very charming and has set his unique aim for today. He needs your help to achieve his objective. Would you come forward to help him out to run on a platform that is full of obstacles? Join Prince Run and be prepared to guide a lovely prince who wants to run and race through the bazaar and cover the maximum distance possible! Try to make him jump over the obstacles and run through obstacles continuously on an adventurous road!

Collect as much gold as possible without being killed and do not forget to upgrade your characters and complete challenges in this brand new adventure game! The coins you collect on your way will help you to purchase upgrades and complete your running adventure in a friendly environment! Grab the flying boots on your way and let your character help fly in the air on a flying carpet without being affected from the obstacles! Take some time to become a master of this runner challenge!

The controls of this html5 running challenge are pretty simple and it also includes seamless gameplay and easy controls. You can browse through our extensive collection of free adventure games and allow yourself to have fun without download. Use your finger to control your character if you play this running challenge in your mobile phone or tablet! Your keyboard and mouse can help you to enjoy it on your desktop. Good luck to pick your best running game and have fun, no download required!
